---
---
<section id="como-funciona" class="relative py-16 px-6">
  <!-- Full-width background image -->
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('/rs.png');background-size:cover;background-position:center;filter:brightness(0.5);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <span style="display:inline-block;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#07ffd2;">Como funciona</span>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.2rem);font-weight:600;color:white;margin-top:0.5rem;">5 passos para sua residência fiscal</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-5">
      {[
        { n:'01', icon:`<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>`, title:'Consulta gratuita', desc:'Entendemos seu perfil e desenhamos a estratégia ideal.' },
        { n:'02', icon:`<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>`, title:'Documentação', desc:'Te auxiliamos na preparação de todos os documentos necessários.' },
        { n:'03', icon:`<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8"/>`, title:'1ª viagem a Assunção', desc:'~5 dias úteis para iniciar o processo de residência.' },
        { n:'04', icon:`<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8"/>`, title:'2ª viagem a Assunção', desc:'~5 dias úteis para retirar sua cédula paraguaia.' },
        { n:'05', icon:`<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>`, title:'Você é residente fiscal', desc:'Renda do exterior isenta. Estrutura funcionando.' },
      ].map((step) => (
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.09);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:14px;padding:22px 18px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:600;color:#07ffd2;margin-bottom:12px;">{step.n}</div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:10px;">
            <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" set:html={step.icon}></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:600;color:white;margin-bottom:6px;">{step.title}</h3>
          <p style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:300;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);line-height:1.5;">{step.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:2.5rem;">
      <a href="https://wa.me/5511913062315" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:white;color:#8417aa;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:500;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:8px;transition:all 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#f7f4fa'" onmouseout="this.style.background='white'">
        Começar meu processo
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
